### Update

### Remove

If you want to remove unnecessary rule from your dictionary, you can remove by following steps: 

1. Visit [_data/proofdict][]
2. Remove the file by click ![Delete the file](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)

### Test

You can test your proof-dictionary is valid format.

Run following command:

    npm install
    npm test
